				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">BTW, you probably know this, but Arkanoid uses the background to draw blocks and not sprites. Collisions are checked by masking rounding the ball's position to the block size and looking up that position in a bit array.<br /><br />This doesn't require loops, so it's more efficient than sprites. You can also display a lot more blocks by doing this.</div>

